Class FriendRequestResponse

  • java.lang.Object
    • FriendRequestResponse
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<FriendRequestResponse>

    public class FriendRequestResponse
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<FriendRequestResponse>
    The FriendRequestResponse class is used to allow a client to communicate an answer to a friend request to the server wich in turn conveys this information to the requester.
    Since:
    2017-11-09
